<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><del rend="crossout"><app>
<note place="topleft">
<l><expan cert="medium">R<ex>ecipimus</ex></expan>
<expan cert="medium">C<ex>utis</ex></expan></l>
</note>
</app>
<expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wilhelmstorffer, uns hat fürgelegt Chuncz
                            Wernher, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz er nu newlich,
                            als er von Winsheim herauff füre, <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> armmanne czu Neithartswind über
                                    <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> abgesnyten acker gefaren sey,
                                        <add><expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan></add> in der angefallen
                            und gewündet und auch darümb <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            bekümert <add>hab</add>, das uns unfreuntlich von
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> dunckt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                            daz ir <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> armman <add>schicken</add> wöllet, daz der
                            den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger ledig <add>werde</add>, das
                                    <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> spricht, hab er dem
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> icht <expan>schade<ex>n</ex>s</expan>
                            daran getan, so wolle er im das gern <add>bessern</add>, als
                                        <add><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></add> das recht darümb
                            erkenne; und lat uns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>nativit<ex>atis</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ea</ex>te</expan>
<expan>Ma<ex>r</ex>ie</expan> <expan>a<ex>nno</ex></expan> ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>. </del></ab></div>
